text: Cristina Lopez Aliaga (born 20 October 1982) is a Spanish water polo player. She played at the 2007 World Aquatics Championships, 2009 World Aquatics Championships, 2008 Women's Water Polo World League, and 2009 Women's Water Polo World League.
